#Sonic Collects Rings

## Introduction
We are going to create a game where Sonic needs to collect bouncing coins which will give him one point each!

## Step 1: Create your background and Sonic sprite!
In the ``||Loops: on start||`` block, place a ``||Scene: set background image||`` block. Get creative! You can add palm trees, sand, ocean views, etc.
```blocks 
scene.setBackgroundImage(img`
